did.unittitle: Stanford University, Program in Human Biology, honors theses
did.abstract: Honors theses written by undergraduate students in the Stanford University Program in Human Biology.

repository.label: Repository:
repository.corpname: Department of Special Collections and University Archives

acqinfo.p: This collection was received in several accessions from the Program in Human Biology. Additional theses were received from the Hume Writing Center in 2011.

accessrestrict.head: Information about Access
accessrestrict.p: The collection is open for research; materials must be requested at least 48 hours in advance of intended use. No photocopies may be made.

userestrict.head: Ownership & Copyright
userestrict.p: Copyright is retained by the creator for materials they have authored or otherwise produced. Transmission or reproduction of materials requires the written permission of the copyright owner.

prefercite.head: Cite As
prefercite.p: [Identification of item], Stanford University, Program in Human Biology, Honors Theses (SC4-4102). Dept. of Special Collections and University Archives, Stanford University Libraries, Stanford, Calif.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents note
scopecontent.p: This collection consists of honors theses written by undergraduate students in the Stanford University Program in Human Biology.
